Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該去採訪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好 你真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是直播 還可以重來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有說過海浪會越來越兇猛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把握好時間 人家說後面還會我們幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不狠狠地叫 我醒不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下等一下 再給我30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 15分鐘就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們在外面等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她沒有眉毛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多女生都會修掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那才比較普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們往南走的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會在海上幾處稱為「站點」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收集微生物和海水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為此船上搭載了不少有用的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是採水器和溫鹽深儀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 這就是…採水器…和溫鹽深儀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:30.77,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}採集這類礦石的同時 要調查南極的地質情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}移開點 移開點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麥克風太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.47,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}調查地底數公里的地質層
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.18,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來研究遠古時期地球的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人倒是留著眉毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你聽人家說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了糟了糟了 遲到了遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該往哪邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:53.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康布丁體W7\fs25\bord1\1c&H3C4041&\3c&H4D5F63&\pos(316,276)}女高中生的房間{\i1}！！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:53.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康布丁體W7\fs25\bord1\1c&H3C4041&\3c&H4D5F63&\pos(352,444)}進門前先{\fn華康POP1體W7\1c&H48E8E4&}敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯嗯 等你們好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡也能做甜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然只是用手頭的材料做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就麻煩你們處理那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才說要帶削皮器的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鈴這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有這麼多沒削啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過這種事做起來真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理很喜歡機械式作業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們四個加起來才剛過一馬力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很慢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正知道你們在家不幫家務啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過慢就慢點 別急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別傷到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我畢竟是專業的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是職業廚師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平時是食堂阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}常面對跟你們一樣挑三揀四的顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又要考慮菜單又要下廚做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們加油 早點學會怎麼搭船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼搭船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.67,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天一一〇〇至一七〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船上跑步訓練 逆時針跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以在船上跑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 我們可以出去運動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運動？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}削完了就帶你們出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運動也算隊員的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在這裡跑步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}廣播裡說順時針 就是這個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說逆時針就是反方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不同的日子跑的方向不一樣 要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概要跑多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這沒有絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你們也聽過不少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觀測隊隊員比拼的就是體能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有時得在零下幾十度的環境下作業一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記住這點 好好鍛鍊自己就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽以前也總是會運動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為體能不足而累倒 不僅是自己什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還會要旁邊的人出手來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都到南極了 你們也不想當拖油瓶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 我們也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理還沒搞清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她很快就會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…這麼…大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在這裡走過很多圈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…大家都差不多這個速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人居然也能跑這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外表是個女科學家 體能卻相當不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…慢著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}18
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從南極回去的時候 我們要變成亞馬遜女戰士了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有那麼容易當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 最後一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月 難道你手抬不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是敢做什麼 我可不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康隸書體W5\1c&H3B3836&\3c&HD1DDEE&\frz1.134\pos(542,150)}不會放過你♡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你白癡嗎 你白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浴缸挺大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值得一泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能快點出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海水的刺激性比想像中強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頭髮都變粗糙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以大家才剪頭髮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男的都剃成了光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那我們也剪掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來幫你剪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船上有理髮的工具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球粉碎了也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 我還挺會剪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經常修自己的瀏海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謎團終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}解開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才是那個髮型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@華康特粗楷體\b0\bord0\1c&H60514C&\pos(608,464)\frx356\fry46\frz259.5}用餐時 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@華康特粗楷體\b0\1c&H60514C&\3c&HEBEDE8&\frx358\fry40\pos(496,260)\frz263.3}沒飯牌請找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}渾身黏答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是你沒有好好沖澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為沒時間了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬鈴薯燉肉 是我們削皮的那些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有什麼忘記做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃飯 洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個還沒有定好時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不是日向你們洗澡的時候在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}負責去洗完再來吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 飯都不給吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但當初因為可能會忘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以定好誰值日的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我記得是大家猜拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\1vc(&H929A90&,&H929A90&,&H494D49&,&H494D49&)\frx350\fry340\frz9.372\pos(586,50)}洗衣間 浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\b0\be1\1c&H85734D&\frz3.398\pos(708,268)\frx344\fry358}關於淡水的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康特粗楷體\bord0\fs25\1c&H808885&\pos(544,362)\frz2.28}綜合訓練期間允許使用淡水洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康特粗楷體\bord0\fs25\1c&H808885&\frz2.28\pos(588,438)}（用海水洗也行哦~）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康楷書體W7\bord0\1c&H2A3989&\pos(604,542)\frz359\frx2\fry354}努力省水喔♡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行什麼行啦 結果還不是吃飽飯才洗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來得及不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定累壞了吧 比預想中忙多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是啦 明天開始也是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撐得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能努力吧 也沒有選擇的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺…好噁心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:15.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康儷中黑\fs22\1c&H271DB2&\3c&HA5B5BC&\frz271.1\t(0,5520,0\frz267.1)\frx4\fry6\move(1086,358,1104,374,33,5497)}上完廁所後 請將此閥門逆時針旋轉沖水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:15.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康儷中黑\fs22\1c&H271DB2&\3c&HA5B5BC&\frz271.1\t(0,5520,0\frz267.1)\frx4\fry6\move(964,360,984,376,33,5497)}沖完後將閥門關緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界在旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說話 一說話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們暈船好嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是之前完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暈船藥也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是藥效過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟是藥嘛 藥效早晚會過的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 從來沒坐過這麼久的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃完藥好好睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有就是要好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們大概沒什麼食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覺得吃了也會吐出來 所以不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是不吃飯 體力會越來越跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後會變成要靠吊點滴來補充營養
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了那個地步 再怎麼鍛鍊也沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}準備用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗小姐不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不想在南極扯後腿 就要逼自己吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部吐光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月也全吐光了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你別晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一下子就好 快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在好像停下來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是要採集海水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也叫停…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然弓子小姐說漸漸會習慣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是根本沒有習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs30\t(0,6520,0\fs35)\1c&H4B534F&\frz5.252\move(544,150,436,58,0,6497)}優勝隊伍的獎勵！\N等待您說出願望！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs45\t(0,6520,0\fs50)\1c&H4B534F&\frz6.777\move(278,200,134,112,33,6497)}請踴躍報名♡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs35\t(0,6520,0\fs40)\1c&H2E1999&\frz8.079\move(16,364,-156,312,33,6497)}想要獲得優勝的隊員請自備\N已經發給各位的瑞士刀參加
