Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:34.16,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}前景雖不明朗 但我已決心邁開雙腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:52.51,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}好奇心與你 牽起了我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:21:00.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}溫柔的聲音與眼神 指引著我新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.39,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出這一步 就是啟程的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.89,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出下一步 我們將走遍四方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:13.28,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}向遠方 向遠方 向陌生的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.03,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}我們都要一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:19.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出這一步 拋下作繭自縛的殼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.74,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出下一步 踏向久久尋求的光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:27.74,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}沒錯呀 就今天 向陌生的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:33.82,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}一步又一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要穿越這片海域啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去那片被狂風大浪保護的冰原大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們選擇了去那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼 雨水？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好鹹 這是海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好鹹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恢復精神了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為昨天還看到了鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於學會搭船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你們下了陸地 又會暈陸地了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}左10度 5海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}萬里無雲 見不到鳥兒飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身邊只有無垠的碧波蕩漾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遙望遠眺 也只有地平線的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船聲浪聲傳入耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但看到這片絕景 彷彿天地間安靜了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的眼前便是宇宙一般寧靜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這一刻我相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極就在視線的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在打開大門前 還有一大段旅程呢
Comment: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:23.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:34.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:40.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:51.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:23:02.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:13.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:18.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:24.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:23.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:34.72,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:40.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:51.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:23:02.04,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:13.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:18.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:24.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
